<h2>Why Learn JavaScript?</h2>
<p>
Web development requires knowledge in three languages, and JavaScript is one of them. The other two are HTML for content and CSS for layout. 
</p>
<p>
This tutorial guides you through all versions of JavaScript, starting from the original version to the latest updates.
</p>

<h2>Learning Pace</h2>
<p>
Learning pace depends on you. Take some time off if you find difficulty. Practice is the key to become a proficient developer.
</p>
